\item \code{adjusting_for()} keeps the models whose adjustment set carries every
named covariate (\code{\link[=adjustment_sets]{adjustment_sets()}} shows the sets and their rungs).
\item \code{excluding()} keeps the models whose formulas avoid the named terms
entirely, whatever the role — the way to set aside a mediator or a
collider before laying the rest out.
}

